SUNTRUST MORTGAGE, INC., a Virginia corporation, Appellant,
v.
KAL-MOR-USA, LLC, a Nevada limited liability company, Respondent. No. 70238 Supreme Court of Nevada. FILED APRIL 09, 2018

Dickinson Wright PLLC

Law Offices of Raffi A. Nahabedian

ORDER DISMISSING APPEAL

Pursuant to the stipulation of the parties, and cause appearing, this appeal is dismissed. The parties shall bear their own costs and attorney fees. NRAP 42(b).

It is so ORDERED.
